.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: grapes, zucchini, carrot, corn, junemelon
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror, drama, disaster, romance
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, december, september, may, june
The people have 5 different hobbies: grapesmaster, chess, rock-climbing, drawing, skydiving
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, soul, salsa, electronic, ambient
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating carrot
2. the person watching swedish movies is the fan of salsa
3. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in may
4. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating corn
5. the person eating zucchini is the person who's birthday is in december
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of soul
7. the person eating junemelon is the person who's hobby is chess
8. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle
9. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the fan of gospel
11. the fan of ambients is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess
12. the person who's hobby is grapesmaster is the person who's birthday is in october
13. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is drawing
14. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person eating grapes
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    junemelon	|     grapes	|      carrot	|     zucchini	|     corn	|
| Movie-Genre	|   disaster	|    horror	|    martial-arts	|    drama	|    swedish	|
| Music-Genre		|     gospel	|    ambient	|     soul	|     electronic	|      salsa	|
| Birthday	|    june	|     may	|     september	|    december	|      october	|
| Hobby		|   chess	|    skydiving	|  rock-climbing	|    drawing	|   grapesmaster	|
